# Example only. Never commit the real keystore or passwords.
# The Gradle release build reads equivalent environment variables:
#
# TOXIC_ANDROID_KEYSTORE_PATH=/absolute/path/to/toxic-teddies-upload.jks
# TOXIC_ANDROID_STORE_PASSWORD=replace-me
# TOXIC_ANDROID_KEY_ALIAS=toxic-teddies-upload
# TOXIC_ANDROID_KEY_PASSWORD=replace-me
#
# Google Play App Signing should hold the app-signing key. Keep the upload key
# outside Git and rotate it through Play Console if it is ever compromised.
